
Files in this directory are considered as self-contained. They obey to these
rules:
  - They only include system headers or headers from common/
  - The tree of dependencies is acyclic
  - Each .c file has a unique .h file with the same name (.h files can exists
    without associated .c file)
  - They provide a well defined interface
  - Each .h file starts with a functionnal description of the component
  - They comply with the coding style of the project
